==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Clincher
<hw>Clinch"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who,
or that which, clinches; that which holds fast.</def>
<rj><au>Pope.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That which ends a dispute or controversy; a decisive
argument.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Clincher-built</ent>⟦br⟧
